 <metadata>
  <name>Blue Hills</name>
  <desc>Intervals: Nice rolly TT loop (~7 mi) with a single stoplight. Roads emptiest during workdays and weekends, avoid rush hour at all costs. The route out is nice, with bike paths. </desc>
  <author>
   <name>Tim Beaver</name>
   <link href="https://www.strava.com/athletes/23022900"/>
  </author>
  <link href="https://www.strava.com/routes/9604565"/>
